#org @talk
= Agatha: We meet again, [player].\c\h08ó\nMuch has happened, it seems.

#org @talk2
= I was filled with pride when Blue\ndefeated me and took his rightful\lplace as Champion.\pPride that there was something worth\npreserving in my blood after all.\pBut Red[.]\c\h08ó He seems a different\nbeast altogether[.]

#org @talk3
= I'd never paid much attention to\nthat child, but it's clear I made\la mistake.\pI can understand now why Samuel\nheld him in such high regard all\lthese years[.]

#org @talk4
= To tell you the truth[.]\pI don't quite know what brought it\nout of these kids[.]

#org @talk5
= Well[.] you're looking for Samuel,\naren't you?\c\h08ó I'll say.\pWhen he walked past me just now[.]\c\h08ó\nIt was strange[.]\pHe was ice cold. Didn't say a word.\c\h08ó\nBut there was a glint in his eye.\pThat cultivated, brownnosing\npoliteness had all but disappeared.

#org @talk6
= There was something in him like the\nway he used to be in the old days.\pLike he had a definite purpose he\nwas chasing[.]

#org @talk7
= Do what you must, [player].\c\h08ó\nBut bear in mind[.]\pThat I will honor whoever is the\nrightful Champion.\pAnd I cannot stand behind anyone\nwho interferes with that justice.\pYou've been warned.

